Enum Colour

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Colour>
      • io.github.martindes01.pickcard.Colour
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Colour>

    public enum Colour
extends java.lang.Enum<Colour>
    Colour is the public enumeration of suit colours.

    Each enum constant encapsulates one field.
    The String name is returned using toString().

    The available enum constants are:

    • BLACK
    • BLUE
    • GREEN
    • RED
    • YELLOW
